        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Consistency gap:</span> AI plays at the same level every turn. Humans lose focus, get tired, and make errors under time pressure. Building mental stamina and concentration habits closes this gap.</p></div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/20 hover:border-purple-400 transition-colors"><p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><span class="text-purple-400 font-semibold">Evaluation gap:</span> AI evaluates thousands of moves per turn perfectly. Humans check 5-20 and sometimes miss better options. Systematic move-finding techniques help humans check more efficiently.</p></div>
      </div>
